genresAdvancedInfo.name: flashcore
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Flashcore is a subgenre of breakcore that is known for its short and intense tracks that often last no longer than 30 seconds. The music is characterized by its frantic and chaotic sound, with samples and beats chopped up and rearranged at breakneck speed. Flashcore is a genre that is not for the faint-hearted and is often used as a form of musical shock therapy.
